metadata.name: Pitbullers #1
metadata.description:
Welcome to #PITBULLERS, the first ETH based NFT collection of Pitbull! These 10,000 unique low-poly NFT’s are waiting to be picked up by their owners; do you feel like sailing the ocean with your 4-legged best friend? We got our loyal seaman! What about crossing the desert with a cowboy by your side? Sounds cool, doesn’t it?
    Whatever your desire is, #Pitbullers is finally here!
